name: Kuchisake Panda - KuD-050
description: She is known as female panda with slit mouth. Her beautiful face was torn by a criminal when she got home alone in the night. She died because of blood loss and became a malicious spirit who search for victim to kill. They say, she wandering alone and approaching people in midnight and she ask them "Am I beautiful ?". If they answer it wrong, she will kill them with a knife that used to slit her mouth. Yeah that's her regret, died with her beautiful face damaged but she still want to be aknowledged as beautiful like when she was alive.
